info.description:
Sorry, a breakdown of computer caused a light delay; and the holidays arrive... 
This is thus an intermediate version.

PLUIE uses Internet-Explorer as a GUI for Python, via COM (PyWin32). PLUIE 
targets easy and fast development in preference to complexity. 

Le projet est en français (Project is in french ; translators are welcome).
